This paper deals with the extraction of semantic information from large datasets, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB). The use of Map-Reduce is also a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of semantic web technologies, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL).
